rove your website architecture, you can conduct a site audit, define site goals and objectives, streamline navigation, optimize content, enhance functionality, optimize performance, and continuously test and refine the site architecture over time.<\/p><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<script type=\"application\/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https:\\\/\\\/schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What is website architecture?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"<p>Website architecture refers to the design and structure of a website, including its information hierarchy, navigation, layout, content, functionality, and performance.<\\\/p>\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Why is website architecture important?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"<p>Website architecture is important because it impacts the usability, accessibility, and overall user experience of the site. It also affects search engine optimization (SEO) by making it easier for search engines to crawl and index the site&#8217;s pages.<\\\/p>\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What are the key aspects of website architecture?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"<p>The key aspects of website architecture include information hierarchy, navigation, layout, content, functionality, performance, and scalability.<\\\/p>\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How can website architecture impact SEO?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"<p>Website architecture can impact SEO in several ways, including by improving crawlability, page authority, content organization, internal linking, and user experience.<\\\/p>\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How can I improve my website architecture?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"<p>To improve your website architecture, you can conduct a site audit, define site goals and objectives, streamline navigation, optimize content